In re Resignation of Guilloton.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Guilloton (1994), 69 Ohio St.3d 1218.]

(No. 94-1132 Submitted June 15, 1994 Decided June 20, 1994.)

The resignation of Sheila Kahoe Guilloton of Simsbury, Connecticut, as an attorney, Registration No. 0009707, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
